      [
        "NO"
      ],
      [
        "What’s absolutely sure, is that tomorrow there is no way that I’d go to school."
      ],
      [
        "I want to rest. "
      ],
      [
        "My eyes close, absolutely tired of everything and I let myself drift away to sleep."
      ],
      [
        "I wake up in my room, the warm sun hits my face, making me feel welcomed by the day. "
      ],
      [
        "I sit up and stretch, but a sharp pain makes me flinch my leg. "
      ],
      [
        "Right… I forgot about that."
      ],
      [
        "A wave of sadness invades me as I recall what [Paul] had done to me. "
      ],
      [
        "I struggle a little bit to get dressed and all, but being active makes me feel"
      ],
      [
        "like I’m not a burden at all. "
      ],
      [
        "Helpie came and left me my breakfast. We had some small talk and Helpie then left to clean the house."
      ],
      [
        "I opted to do some homework, since I really didn’t have anything else to do."
      ],
      [
        "Still, my mind doesn’t fully focus on what I’m doing… [Paul] becomes everything that I can think of."
      ],
      [
        "After a while, I am now playing a video game."
      ],
      [
        " I have played it mindlessly and now I’ve almost gotten all its achievements."
      ],
      [
        "Now I just need the two - player ones, but Helpie isn’t the best one to play games with."
      ],
      [
        "Their fast calculations and speed always make them win."
      ],
      [
        "I am milliseconds away from starting a new game, when I hear my doorbell ring."
      ],
      [
        "I wait for a little bit, when Helpie opens my door. "
      ],
      [
        "[tn], It’s [Paul]. [He] says [he] wants to talk to you…"
      ],
      [
        "should I let [him] in? "
      ],
      [
        "Yes… let [him] in. "
      ],
      [
        "Helpie lets [Paul] in, and [he] quickly comes to me."
      ],
      [
        "[He] hands me a box full of my favorite candies and kneels to be at my level."
      ],
      [
        "I gesture for Helpie to let us have some privacy."
      ],
      [
        "[tn], I- I’m so sorry. For yesterday, for everything. I’ve been an idiot."
      ],
      [
        "It’s just that I was so afraid of everything. Of not passing the grades, of you getting hurt, that I lost control…"
      ],
      [
        "I- I promise I will never do anything like that again, I will never let you down…"
      ],
      [
        "please, can you forgive me?"
      ]
